snippet.title: kukun kun kut - Wario no Mori Event Version 2 Magazine (1 of ???)
snippet.description:
Source: ゲーム虎の大穴スペシャル 1995年7月27日
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q0VREpsyum4

(Previous upload had limited ads so here's a freebie for you)
In some of kukun kun's recent uploads there are magazines promoting "Wario no Mori Event Version 2", which was ROM dumped some time ago. These magazines may give additional context into the game's existence, so I clipped them and put them up here. They seem to cover elements like game rules - even ones basic to Wario's Woods buffs.

Thanks for watching! As with all YouTube channels, likes, subscriptions and comments are welcome - but I presume that is to be expected, yes?

If you want to show your support in other ways, feel free to use StreamLabs!
